column5: LR 12-sep-12*** As agreed by the project manager, this gauge can be waivered, the defect is minimal and at 100degC. calibration failure waivered.
***LRossini - 12-oct-12*** THe test failed due to battery issue. The battery issue is investigate on SQ 20121003124838 and IFR 382807 . The gauge is OK, need to repeat CAT. TFL closed.
